videos.headline: Stevenson spins his way in  for 24-yard TD
videos.description: Houston's D'Eriq King passes to Marquez Stevenson, who spins his way in  for a 24-yard TD.

videos.headline: D'Eriq King muscles his way in for TD
videos.description: D'Eriq King muscles his way in for a short touchdown run to give Houston a 14-0 lead on Arizona.

videos.headline: Houston's Stevenson drops potential TD
videos.description: Marquez Stevenson is open and drops a perfect potential touchdown pass from his quarterback.

videos.headline: Oliver, Houston stop Arizona on 4th down
videos.description: Ed Oliver and Houston stop Arizona's Gary Brightwell on fourth down.

videos.headline: Houston's Smith catches 13-yard strike for TD
videos.description: Houston's Bryson Smith catches a laser beam from D'Eriq King for a 13-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Arizona's center gives Oliver head tap
videos.description: Ed Oliver's neutral zone infraction is met with a slap on the helmet from the Arizona center.

videos.headline: Houston's King escapes and tosses 18-yard TD
videos.description:
D'Eriq King escapes the rush and throws an
 18-yard touchdown pass to Keith Corbin.

videos.headline: Arizona's Tate throws 2nd INT of game
videos.description: Khalil Tate throws his second interception of the game as Houston's Gary Davis comes up with the pick..

videos.headline: Arizona's Smith finds pay dirt on 1-yard TD
videos.description: Darrius Smith slashes up the middle for a 1-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Houston comes up with 4th-down goal-line stand
videos.description: Houston's defense steps up and stops Arizona at the goal line on fourth down.

videos.headline: Houston's King runs untouched for 4-yard touchdown
videos.description: D'Eriq King runs around the corner for a 4-yard touchdown
